entries.femaleVariant: Why the fuck isn't it?
You created Soulkiller. You handed Arasaka a fuckin' super weapon that dismantled me, you and half the 'runners in Night City!
Your death was of your own making.
Jesus, Alt, I dove in after you. Gonna tell me now this ain't your problem?
It is not. The Alt Cunningham you strove to save in Arasaka Tower no longer exists.
This should be obvious to you as you were responsible for her death.
Voodoo Boys – what about them?
They shall let you pass unharmed. Those were our terms.
Alt, before you leave, we gotta talk. Just you and me.
What of Brigitte and the Voodoo Boys?
I was forced to purge them. NetWatch was exploiting their BBS.
"Purge?" Mean they're dead, all of them?
What'd you do with Brigitte? She still alive?
Yes – but she is not needed at the moment.
What do you want?
Brigitte – what'd she want from you in exchange for Johnny?
And why'd they wanna go out there?
The corporation-controlled net is now nearly as unstable as it was before the Blackwall's creation.
The Voodoo Boys wished to use this to their advantage – to fight on our side when the time comes.
"Your side" meaning that of free AIs? That even possible?
entries.maleVariant: "Your side" meanin' that of free AIs? That even possible?

entries.femaleVariant: That I guarantee her and her clan's safety beyond the Blackwall.
If they prepare appropriately.
No. That will not be possible.
Brigitte – what'd she want from you in exchange for Johnny?
That I guarantee her and her clan's safety beyond the Blackwall.
And what'd they wanna find out there?
The corporation-controlled net is now nearly as unstable as it was before the Blackwall's creation.
The Voodoo Boys wished to use this to their advantage – to fight on our side when the time comes.
Not actually gonna feel bad for 'em, are ya?
NetWatch propaganda has been effective. Do you see me as a demon who requires a pact signed in blood?
Johnny's got it planned out. Question is your fee.
The Relic is killing me.
Don't know who you are.
Just wanna survive, live on.
Got no clue who you are now. Know a little about who you were.
Listen, I'm just tryna survive.
And Johnny, that he was important to you, while I'm no one. So I'm askin' – what's it gonna cost?
I cannot help you.
Relax, lemme handle this.
Johnny.
Came through the Blackwall to meet me… That mean we're good, things're chill between us?
I have recognized your engram code, but I do not know why you are here.
V, this is Alt – best netrunner Night City's ever seen.
My fault, I brought NetWatch here.
What about the Voodoo Boys?
What did Brigitte want from you?
Dammit. I brought NetWatch here. Agent I dealt with must've slipped me a tracker that led 'em right in.
entries.maleVariant: Dammit! I brought NetWatch here. Agent I dealt with must've slipped me a tracker that led 'em right in.

entries.femaleVariant: Prolly how they got to you.
It matters not. The entire subnet was destroyed.
Alt...
You pulled us outta there – that mean you and us, we're OK, everything's chill?
I have recognized your engram code, but I do not know why you are here.
What's the price I gotta pay for you to save my life?
What did the VDBs want for in exchange for the construct?
What'd you do with Brigitte?
NetWatch cannot touch me here.
NetWatch was well prepared this time.
To give ya a chance to pay me back for gettin' you outta Arasaka Tower.
Alt, this is V – you need to save her life.
entries.maleVariant: Alt, this is V – you need to save his life.

entries.femaleVariant: So you can pay me back for gettin' you outta Arasaka Tower.
V, this is Alt – best netrunner Night City's ever seen.
Alt, this is V – you need to save her life.
entries.maleVariant: Alt, this is V – you need to save his life.

entries.femaleVariant: The Relic is killing me.
As you can see, Johnny's got it all thought out.
But there's the question of what you'll want in return.
To save my life… what's it gonna cost?
The chip, the Relic, it's killin' me. Construct on it is wormin' its way through my neural system.
entries.maleVariant: This chip, the Relic, it's killin' me. Construct on it is wormin' its way through my neural system.

entries.femaleVariant: I see this. But why is it my problem?
OK, I get it, you hate Johnny's guts. But what about me?
I cannot help you.
Wasn't Johnny's fault.
OK, got a beef with Johnny, but what about me?
Your death wasn't Johnny's fault.
How could you know?
Seen you in his memories… It was an accident.
What you saw was his subjective view of what happened. A warped account of events he locked away in his subconscious and replayed time and again.
It bears no resemblance to the truth.
If you're not Alt, who are you?
I use her engramatic data.
Really. You find this "icy bitch" aspect in there, too?
Can't? Or won't?
Mind unloadin' this baggage later?
Wasn't sure what to expect from a meeting with an AI, but it sure wasn't a digital spat.
How's that help me, exactly?
Well, didn't make it any worse.
entries.maleVariant: Aa, didn't make it any worse.

entries.femaleVariant: Maybe you two can hash this out later?
What? You created Soulkiller.
Can't. To attempt to do so, I would need access to more advanced technology.
Interesting. Brigitte said it'd be possible.
What? But it's your tech, you created Soulkiller.
Interesting... Brigitte claimed she alone could help me.
The Voodoo Boys deceived you.
Why'm I not surprised?
The program I created has little in common with how Arasaka has since repurposed it.
Fine... So how about Mikoshi? That advanced enough for ya?
If I could gain access to Mikoshi, it would cease to exist.
What can you do for me, exactly?
Good, we can work with that. We'll get you inside Mikoshi, and you'll help V – deal?
City's best netrunner can't break into Mikoshi on her own?
What can you do for me, exactly?
With the Soulkiller resident inside Mikoshi, I will create a construct of you, then disentangle your neural network from Johnny's.
Everyone I've met so far says I'm too far gone.
entries.maleVariant: Everyone I've met so far's said I'm too far gone.

entries.femaleVariant: By "everyone" you mean Hellman? Saburo's personal assmunch?
Best 'runner Night City's ever seen can't bust into Mikoshi on her own?
I am a well known threat there. They have a layer of black ICE with my name on it, literally.
I refuse to be caged in there ever again.
Kinda like a custom-made prison jumpsuit…
So... you'll save my life but flatline me along the way?
Your consciousness, neural engrams, will be recorded as data. The rest will cease to exist.
The rest?
The soul. I did not grant the program its name, but Soulkiller does precisely what it promises to do.
Christ, I don't wanna listen to this bullshit.
V just hops back into her body, right? Nothin' changes.
entries.maleVariant: V just hops back into his body, right? Nothin' changes.

entries.femaleVariant: Everything changes. You know this well.
OK, so we got a plan.
Gotta kill me to save me?
Right, so we got a plan.
But how will you reach Mikoshi? I've created armies that failed to breach it.
They were children of the Net – there's your problem.
We're bankin' on the human factor.
V's the most sociable fucker I've ever met. Has powerful friends – mercs, nomads…
We'll crack a window, slip you into Mikoshi.
Believe it or not, folks at the Afterlife adore V. They'll have her back.
entries.maleVariant: Believe it or not, folks at the Afterlife adore V. They'll have his back.

entries.femaleVariant: V's got a big, dusty nomad family. And they'll do anything for her.
entries.maleVariant: V's got a big, dusty nomad family. And they'll do anything for him.

entries.femaleVariant: Are we agreed?
Johnny's right.
So, we agreed?
Johnny's right. We can do this.
You trust him deeply, I see.
Yes, we are agreed. Find a path into Mikoshi, I shall prepare a program to help you navigate the localnet.
How'll I contact you once I'm ready?
This is a BBS address. It will be our secure communication channel.
You don't?
As you are the "human factor," it is with you that I will set terms.
Johnny gets goin', exaggerates sometimes.
Johnny... embellishes, case you hadn't noticed.
entries.maleVariant: Johnny, uh... embellishes, in case you hadn't noticed.

entries.femaleVariant: You don't trust him, which is fine, but you have my word we'll slip you inside Mikoshi while keepin' you outta harm's way.
I believe this "human factor" and I have things in common.
I shall then inject your engram back into your mortal form.
What happened out there? Couldn't just take 'em out?
Gotta be Mosley, the fucker.
Switched things up on the sly, replacin' the Voodoos' virus with his own brand of rot.
We will talk here.
So if you're not Alt, who are you?
It's really you.
What do you expect from me? This I can't fathom.
Your projection in cyberspace… it's interesting.
Your appearance here – an unnecessary risk.
